title: Top 15 Most Beautiful Women In The World!

json.text: Nothing makes a woman more beautiful than the belief that she is beautiful, and with
that said let’s remember every woman is her own kind of beauty.
So you know why we said that?
We are unveiling the list of the most beautiful women around the globe.
You are a true beauty in yourself and you don’t want us to tell you that but these
15 women rule the hearts of the universe.
So let the countdown to the most celebrated beauties begin!
Number 15.
Irene Esser Never doubt the beauty of Miss Venezuela!
Irene has been a part of the Miss Universe pageant 2012 where she ended up as the second
runner up; can you now question her beauty?
She stands tall at 5 feet 10 inches with a perfectly carved figure and even better facial
features.
Her skin tone along with her dark hair makes for an exotic appearance!
Number 14.
Taylor Swift The highest paid singer in the world is also
among the most beautiful women, how about that?
She seems to work on her voice as much as her looks!
The blue eyed blonde has an impressive height of 5’10’’ and a slim physique to match.
God took a lot of extra time while designing her, go girl go!
Number 13.
Pia Wurtzbach Crowned as Miss Universe 2015, Pia is gorgeous
without a doubt.
The German-Filipino actress is a brunette with an hour glass figure supported on her
5 feet 8 inch frame.
Her deep brown eyes, perfectly sculpted nose and a subtle jawline give her an edge over
the others.
You can’t help but be mesmerized by her beauty!
Number 12.
Im Jin-ah The South Korean beauty, better known by her
stage name, Nana is a stunner!
Would you believe us if we say that apart from being a singer and an actress, she is
also a licensed makeup artist?
No wonder she looks impeccable always!
She can enchant you with her porcelain doll like looks and that is surely path breaking!
Number 11.
Selena Gomez This American singer and actress definitely
makes it to the list of the most beautiful women.
The brunette has a perfect figure that adds to her facial charm.
Gomez has a huge fan following, all thanks to her singing talent but that’s not all.
Her good looks have a major role to play in this.
You go girl, we love you!
Number 10.
Lyndsy Fonseca Remember Penny Mosby from How I Met Your Mother
or Dylan Mayfair from the third season of Desperate Housewives?
We bet you can’t say no to this gorgeous American actress!
This woman was listed on Maxim Hot 100 for two consecutive years and that my friend is
no joke.
There’s no way we are denying that lovely smile a spot here!
Number 9.
Alexandra Daddario This 31 year old American actress and model
recently won a lot of hearts through her role as Summer Quinn in the Hollywood movie Baywatch.
Her mystic blue eyes never miss to pull you towards them and then her GQ Mexico magazine
cover was enough to get temperatures soaring.
That bikini shot got more than 200 thousand likes in just a week!
Now can you question her presence on this list?
Number 8.
Fahriye Evcen How can we not put this Turkish actress on
this list?
The brunette with her perfectly sculpted jawline, enchanting smile and deep eyes just casts
a spell on everyone and leaves little to question her beauty.
You do remember her role as Necla Tekin in Yaprak Dökümü, didn’t she mesmerize you?
Her fluency in Turkish, German, Spanish and English comes as a bonus!
Number 7.
Margot Robbie You couldn’t have missed the pretty blonde
from ‘The Wolf Of The Wall Street’.
This young 27 year old Australian actress has marveled us with her bold and powerful
personality.
After she played Harley Quinn in Suicide Squad, she indeed has told us what she is capable
of.
What can we say when Brad Pitt himself feels that she is the hottest girl around?
Number 6.
Dakota Johnson Did you really think Anastasia Steele from
Fifty Shades Of Grey and its sequel, will not make it to this list?
After all, the girl has inherited her good looks from her actor parents, Melanie Griffith
and Don Johnson!
My my, her intense eyes compliment her slender body very well, making her a lethal cocktail!
Number 5.
Emma Watson Our very own Hermione Granger has come a long
way from 2001 and with her avatar in Beauty and the Beast, not many can question her presence
on this list!
This British actress has got a body to kill for but her cuteness overshadows everything.
There is no doubt about her being the youth icon and yes, all the 90s guys have had a
secret crush over her!
Number 4.
Taylor Hill The youngest Victoria’s Secret Angel is
just 21 years old and already a heart throb!
Hill is tall with the best body ever and a pair of dreamy eyes.
Those luscious lips have a tale to tell and her lingerie photoshoots are instant hits.
No wonder she has 7.6 million followers on Instagram.
That girl oozes beauty from every angle you can take a peek at!
Number 3.
Priyanka Chopra This dusky Indian beauty has shown the world
what she can achieve with her talent coupled with stunning looks!
After being actively involved in Bollywood, PC made the big jump with TV series Quantico
and then her Hollywood debut, Baywatch crowned her a true star.
Her perfect body and striking facial features have left us awestruck!
Number 2.
Beyonce The American singer and songwriter has won
5 Grammy Awards for her exceptional talent but we aren’t talking about that here.
This lady surely possesses some exotic beauty traits for she is loved and celebrated throughout
the world.
You know a woman is truly beautiful when she can practically slay in her baby bump!
Number 1.
Liza Soberano The young Filipino-American beauty makes it
to number one with her cute looks.
She started her career with television but moved on to movies and looking at her, this
seems just the obvious thing!
Her brown eyes match the shade of her hair and her perfectly formed lips curl into an
enchanting smile.
You just can’t have enough of her beauty, she is simply stunning!
There are plenty of gorgeous ladies out there so would you want to add on to the list?
Tell us in the comment section below.
